          "error_type": "concept_gap",
          "note": "This is the Identity Property"
        },
        "D": {
          "error_type": "concept_gap",
          "note": "This is place value decomposition, not a property"
        }
      },
      "solution_steps": [
        "Commutative Property: you can change the ORDER of addends",
        "15 + 28 = 28 + 15 — the order changed, the sum stays the same"
      ],
      "hint": "Commutative means you can switch the order.",
      "verification": "Go Math p.21 — Commutative Property definition",
      "correct_answer": "A"
